item.title: WELCOME TO ARTISAN DENTAL GROUP!
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded:
You want convenience. Your family wants comfort. And you all want caring and competent people to deliver the exceptional dentistry you deserve. You just found all that – and more – at Artisan Dental Group, where you and your needs really do come first.

It is our vision to create a uniquely fun and friendly atmosphere in our office – an atmosphere in which anyone, from toddlers to great grandparents, feels right at home.

Why do we think this is so important? It’s just dentistry, something you have to do but will probably never enjoy, right? Absolutely not! Our patients actually enjoy their visits with us and that helps them stay consistent in their care, and that helps keep their mouths and their bodies healthier for life!

INTELLIGENT TECHNOLOGY. ARTISTIC CARE.

While we do believe in the power of compassion and coziness, we aren’t just here to help you love your dentistry – we are here to help you love your smile too! Dr. Callejo is a little bit of a nerd when it comes to technology, and that’s a good thing! Our patients love the way our innovative tools and gadgets not only make screenings and procedures easier, they make them more accurate and effective too. When you add that to Dr. Callejo’s outstanding artistry and experience, you know you have the perfect combination of art and science. If this sounds like the care you have been wishing… hoping… even dreaming of, call us today! We are right here, waiting to see you smile!

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: COMPLETE DENTAL CARE FOR YOUR FAMILY
OUR KETTERING AND BELMONT PRACTICES HAVE EVERYTHING YOU NEED

If you’ve been searching for a dental practice for your entire family, look no further. When it comes to a healthy smile, Dr. Callejo provides everything that you and your family could ever need. Our practices have served more than three generations of patients, because they just keep coming back! Whatever your needs, cosmetic, reconstructive, or structural, we will address them all. item.title: COSMETIC DENTISTRY
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded:
RESTORING SELF-CONFIDENCE AND BEAUTIFUL SMILES EACH DAY

Being self-conscious about your teeth could prevent you from making new friends, getting a job, networking effectively, or even laughing often. Dr. Callejo wants to help you reclaim the joy in your life, so we work hard to bring you treatments and therapies that will put the glisten back on your grin. There’s no one right cosmetic treatment for everyone. That’s why we offer a combination of cosmetic services for you to choose from:

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: A SMILE YOUR COULD BE PROUD OF

You deserve a smile you’re proud of. Crooked, discolored, or misshapen teeth are easily corrected with our cosmetic dental options. We offer porcelain veneers, teeth whitening, and composite bonding to enhance your smile and change your life. Dr. Callejo even offers Botox and Juvederm! [Read more…]

Dr. Callejo is a licensed sedation dentist in Ohio. You may select from inhalation, oral, or conscious IV sedation during your dental treatment. With sedation dentistry, we enhance your level of comfort, and keep your mind at ease when you’re anxious or if you need a lot of procedures. [Read more…]

item.title: Porcelain Veneers
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: Our veneers go over the front of the teeth to correct the appearance of teeth that are broken, misshapen, gapped, or severely discolored. Each veneer is custom designed to the shape, color, and size you prefer to help you achieve the smile of your dreams.

Irregular gumlines, gummy smiles, or uneven teeth can impact the overall look of your smile. By gently reshaping gum tissue and the edges of your teeth, we can make your smile full and even from ear to ear. . Gum and tooth recontouring is simple, effective, and produces instant results.

item.title: Minimal Prep Veneers
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: This less-invasive dental veneer is a completely reversible treatment that offers a more translucent appearance. Minimal prep veneers are placed over gently conditioned teeth, to give you a completely new smile.

Are you bothered by a small gap, irregular edge, or a chip in one or two of your teeth? Composite bonding is an excellent way to rebuild your tooth by using tooth-colored restorative materials. The end result looks just like a full, healthy tooth.

item.title: Full-Mouth Restoration
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: Has it been years since you’ve seen a dentist? Do you have several teeth that are breaking down or wearing away? Our full-mouth restoration therapy addresses your mouth as a whole. You and Dr. Callejo will formulate a treatment plan to return your mouth to optimal health and beauty.

item.title: Smile Whitening
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: It’s normal for your smile to darken over time, especially if you drink coffee, soda, red wine or use tobacco products. Our safe and effective professional teeth whitening treatments help lift years of stain and make your smile brighter. You may choose from our take-home, custom whitening trays that produce full results within 10-14 days, or our in-office whitening treatment that brightens your smile in just one hour.

item.title: Crown Lengthening
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: Sometimes, broken or badly damaged teeth can still be restored. In our crown-lengthening procedure, Dr. Callejo removes a small amount of gum tissue around the tooth so that fixed restorations like crowns or bridges can be placed. Crown lengthening may also be used for management of gum disease, by making it easier to keep the areas around your teeth clean and free of bacteria.

item.title: Injectables
item.dc:creator: Admin
item.content:encoded: In addition to our dental cosmetic services, we offer additional service to enhance your face. Dr. Callejo has taken multiple courses on facial sculpting using Botox and dermal fillers and is a certified Botox, Juvederm, and Restylane provider. He is uniquely qualified to provide these services – after all, who knows your facial structure better than your dentist? Better yet, we can provide all of these services right here in our comfortable and convenient office. Why not surround your beautiful smile with youthful and glowing features? Ask us about our facial injectables today!
